title: War Party- 80`s Billy Wirth, Kevin Dillon
description:
Movie Description
A century-old feud is revived when a small town decides to re-enact the most important event in it&#039;s history. When the event, intended to pay homage to a tribe of Indians massacred by the U.S. Cavalry, results in the bloody murder of a young Indian, the day of remembrance becomes a war of revenge.

Credits 
Cast: Billy Wirth, Kevin Dillon 
Director: Franc Roddam 

Industry Reviews
"...WAR PARTY shapes up to be one of the shrewdest, uncanniest, nerviest action pictures of the year..."
Los Angeles Times - Chris Willman (09/29/1989)
